pv.name: iocjscalers1:LOAD
pv.description: Heavy CPU Load on Sector 1 JScalers

guidance.title: Guidance
guidance.details: This usually means a communications error with the tcp server on one of the DAQ crates. Try to Reboot iocjscaler1 from the JScaler IOC Health screen
